name: BE LOUD
description:
This past few days, with me being a corporate slave, i feel like i don't really have the time to do what i love which is art. It keeps me from being tranquil and at peace but everyday i try to fight it. Everytime i get the chance to do someting creative, i pour my soul into doing whatever it is. This is my only way to keep the fire going. Nevertheless, i believe with what the Universe planned for me. I truly hold on to the idea that i can get pass all the challenges and be what i've always wanted to be; a full time artist. That is why i will never get tired to screaming what i treasure into the Universe until i get it. 

I hope you'll be with me in this journey.

8000X10000px
Original artwork by Vilton
